      "content": "i see. i'm just wondering though, what about option B? it's definitely got a lot of culture and people from all over the world, which some luxury brands might see as 'cultured' or 'sophisticated' in a modern way. why wouldn't that work for a high-end brochure compared to Oakwood?",
